            <div class="row justify-content-center mt-3">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <p class="text-center mb-0 mt-4">
                        Copyright &copy;2024. All rights reserved | This portfolio is crafted with <span class="ti-heart fg-theme-red"></span> by
